</div><p>和两层嵌套的 decorator 相比，3 层嵌套的效果是这样的:</p>
<div class="language-py" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="py" data-title="py" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre v-pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#56B6C2">>>></span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF"> now </span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#56B6C2">=</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF"> log</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379">'execute'</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF">)(now)</span></span></code></pre>
